		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Patricia Foster</span></strong>, a professor in the <span class="smallcaps">MFA</span> program at the University of Iowa, is the editor of four essay collections and the author of the nonfiction books <em>All the Lost Girls</em> and <em>Just beneath My Skin</em>. She recently drove a thousand miles with her husband to the ocean in order to write about life in Iowa. She is working on a book about illness and marriage.</p><a href="/contributors/patricia-foster" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
